  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">salvaged</span> upgrade for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit</span>. Use <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> to begin upgrade <VAL_ON>installation process<>.<br><br>Constructed by the <TRANS_BUI>Autophage<>, this technology package is the result of a high degree of engineering improvisation. As a one-of-a-kind piece of repurposed technology, its exact effect upon suit performance is hard to determine prior to installation within the Exosuit's systems.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一个<span class=\"name name-stellar\">回收</span>的<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装</span>升级组件。使用<VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>启动升级<VAL_ON>安装流程<>。<br><br>该技术包由<TRANS_BUI>自噬体<>制造，是即兴工程创作的成果。在安装到套装系统之前，很难预知这项独一无二的改造技术对套装性能的具体影响。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝</span>的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">回收</span>升級。使用 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> 即可開始升級<VAL_ON>安裝程序<>。<br><br>此科技套組由<TRANS_BUI>自噬<>製作，是高度即興創作的工程學產物。這個獨一無二的改裝技術元件，在安裝到強化套裝系統之前，較難預測對套裝效能的影響。"
  },
